{"tid":1182958,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"木結他fingerstyle：手指vs指甲","createTime":"2019-06-02T14:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T06:58:02.000Z","uid":235939,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"307b6f5b7572730f4906c2d1a22a096de414849e","tid":1182958,"uid":235939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:29:12.000Z","msg":"話說小弟呢排開始玩fingerstyle(自學)，開頭都係用開手指黎彈(冇留指甲)，後來發現有nail attack呢樣野之後就開始留指甲黎練下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁之後我先發現有指甲同冇指甲彈出黎嘅聲差好遠，有指甲嘅聲bright好多但音量好難控制(因為我廢，成日彈到爆聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n但我見YouTube好多玩fingerstyle嘅結他手都留到好長指甲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇高手可以指教一下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 教下我點樣可以用指甲黎彈fingerstyle又smooth又bright又好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d774548d5b71671a8353dec6161b6397dd01cf1","tid":1182958,"uid":214570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"唔好留太長同埋要搵野磨架"},{"pid":"13cb0cb7283716cbac4db3400d2e932c2a72e8fc","tid":1182958,"uid":235939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d774548d5b71671a8353dec6161b6397dd01cf1","tid":1182958,"uid":214570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"唔好留太長同埋要搵野磨架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:35:51.000Z","msg":"用指甲鉗磨得唔得架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋想請教埋巴打，用指甲嘅彈法係咪同用手指一樣架咋？定要細力d，我一用力佢就勁大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e4598f26316d8a932991b4a3f47becfdb5f90f","tid":1182958,"uid":9932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:25:11.000Z","msg":"指甲每個人都唔同<br />\n要自己慢慢磨出屬於自己既形狀<br />\n<br />\n爆聲會唔會係你枝結他痴fret?<br />\n或者可以換條high tension弦