moji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:23:25.000Z","msg":"0.12係high tension無錯<br />\n巴打係邊條弦會爆?<br />\n<br />\n我正常嘅彈法只會姆指掂到小小肉<br />\n主要都係指甲彈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:28:11.000Z","msg":"多數係1 2弦爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實用指甲彈個手勢應該係點樣？<br />\n我上網睇d人係同條弦平行咁彈，但我咁彈就會爆聲，反而斜斜地一隻手咁彈就冇咁爆<br />\n究竟邊款彈法先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平行個樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJu39pD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJu39pD.png&h=535a5f5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:53:50.000Z","msg":"唔記得講我係彈古典<br />\n指甲可能同方便掃chord嘅形狀有啲唔同<br />\n<br />\n古典正常放鬆擺法係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5awYYoF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5awYYoF.png&h=ae3b3683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我指甲長度大約長呢個小小<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CuMVgap.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCuMVgap.png&h=58941b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n彈嘅時候可以跟圖一形狀放<br />\n然後好似渣拳頭咁齊奏<br />\n大力空弦做到又齊又唔爆就記低個感覺<br />\n呢個係你枝結他暫時最大聲量<br />\n<br />\n如果只係12弦爆應該只係太用力<br />\n6條弦用嘅力度都唔同<br />\n用唔同手指彈同一條弦都要用唔同力度<br />\n<br />\n至於正確手形<br />\n如果有經濟能力<br />\n最好都係搵個&rdquo;好老師&rdquo;打好基礎<br />\nYouTube有好多手勢都係錯到離曬譜<br />\n同埋就咁睇片好難知道自己姿勢、發力、角度有無問題"},{"pid":"0fcdbce169f639c7a14480b806542040f3d96c8e","tid":1182958,"uid":235939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84f9b0c60c0b420a7b6103694cae480c35743dca","tid":1182958,"uid":9932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41b08e6bc4d850f8fb14227812931a4bf27d207e","tid":1182958,"uid":235939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95f22727aa22ae6368075dd0529060aab97d970a","tid":1182958,"uid":9932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:23:25.000Z","msg":"0.12係high tension無錯<br />\n巴打係邊條弦會爆?<br />\n<br />\n我正常嘅彈法只會姆指掂到小小肉<br />\n主要都係指甲彈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:28:11.000Z","msg":"多數係1 2弦爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實用指甲彈個手勢應該係點樣？<br />\n我上網睇d人係同條弦平行咁彈，但我咁彈就會爆聲，反而斜斜地一隻手咁彈就冇咁爆<br />\n究竟邊款彈法先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平行個樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJu39pD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJu39pD.png&h=535a5f5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:53:50.000Z","msg":"唔記得講我係彈古典<br />\n指甲可能同方便掃chord嘅形狀有啲唔同<br />\n<br />\n古典正常放鬆擺法係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5awYYoF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5awYYoF.png&h=ae3b3683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我指甲長度大約長呢個小小<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CuMVgap.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCuMVgap.png&h=58941b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n彈嘅時候可以跟圖一形狀放<br />\n然後好似渣拳頭咁齊奏<br />\n大力空弦做到又齊又唔爆就記低個感覺<br />\n呢個係你枝結他暫時最大聲量<br />\n<br />\n如果只係12弦爆應該只係太用力<br />\n6條弦用嘅力度都唔同<br />\n用唔同手指彈同一條弦都要用唔同力度<br />\n<br />\n至於正確手形<br />\n如果有經濟能力<br />\n最好都係搵個&rdquo;好老師&rdquo;打好基礎<br />\nYouTube有好多手勢都係錯到離曬譜<br />\n同埋就咁睇片好難知道自己姿勢、發力、角度有無問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T10:37:11.000Z","msg":"感謝巴打指導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發現自己問題應該係彈條弦果陣隻手指隊得太入(慣左咁用手指彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，慢慢習慣下淨係用指甲黎撥條弦先(宜家覺得好唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n同埋可能我指甲應該都係留得太短<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547b815d2391710e2fe5e018ac6fcd3e3eee3ed1","tid":1182958,"uid":9932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0fcdbce169f639c7a14480b806542040f3d96c8e","tid":1182958,"uid":235939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84